Class AbstractBulkResources<T extends ModelInfo>

  • java.lang.Object

    Orders

    public abstract class AbstractBulkResources<T extends ModelInfo>
extends AbstractResources<T>
    Base class for all resources types that support bulk operations. This overrides the getByIds(java.util.Collection) method to query through the bulk API for improved performance.
